title: Bug 6322 - All types dialog shows obfuscated classes
description: Bug 6322 - The All types dialog in JDK 1.4 includes obfuscated classes (a, a1, b, c, d) etc.
OB: The All types dialog in JDK 1.4 is displaying obfuscated classes.
EB: The All types dialog in JDK 1.4 should not display obfuscated classes.
SR: Options: a) Sort lower case class names after the ones that start with a capital letter, b) Filter out obfuscated classes completely. I suggest implementing option a) to address this issue.
